{"tid":1314921,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"沙田新安全點","createTime":"2019-07-14T11:26:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T11:26:33.000Z","uid":275595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d9a841d4bc2cce299ca33b1870d7b76412f7969b","tid":1314921,"uid":275595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T11:26:33.000Z","msg":"【⚠️放映會場地將改作成安全點】<br />\n<br />\n鑒於警方使用不斷提升增援，一帶路段仍未解封，導致放映器材未能進場，原定八時舉辦的放映會將會暫停。<br />\n<br />\n同時，因放映會位置（即大會堂百步梯）已獲不反對通知書批准為合法集會（至晚上十一時），警方將不能隨意到場清場。為保障示威者安全，改作和平集會。❗️如有需要示威者可逃生到該處暫避。❗️<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ShatinCommons/?__tn__=%2Cd%2CP-R&amp;eid=ARA8srHkInNvMs81uPRmKhmKyk7iJoYsYpyV3DYgfycl4CSTe1feP10PtAP1zdv-eE-YlZ06SeZZO8V4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FShatinCommons%2F%3F__tn__%3D%252Cd%252CP-R%26eid%3DARA8srHkInNvMs81uPRmKhmKyk7iJoYsYpyV3DYgfycl4CSTe1feP10PtAP1zdv-eE-YlZ06SeZZO8V4&d=05%2BDYq1PAX1syIB%2FutXPalpzQI%2FFghXCkDWT3grjsfs%3D&h=66fdf38f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/ShatinCommons/?__tn__=%2Cd%2CP-R&amp;eid=ARA8srHkInNvMs81uPRmKhmKyk7iJoYsYpyV3DYgfycl4CSTe1feP10PtAP1zdv-eE-YlZ06SeZZO8V4</a>"}]}